WEBVTT

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.280
Chen Fan

00:01:07.719 --> 00:01:10.319
Who did you get into a fight with?

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:13.319
Actually, I have something to tell you.

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:14.959
You asked me and Brother Honghai

00:01:14.959 --> 00:01:15.920
to look into the game proposal.

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:18.040
I feel like something's off.

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:19.120
He is definitely off.

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:19.480
Right?

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:21.159
We haven't even worked out the game framework,

00:01:21.159 --> 00:01:22.400
and he's always thinking about how to monetize.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:23.840
Isn't that thinking a bit too twisted?

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.879
It's not just his game logic that's twisted.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:28.280
I'll go talk to him in a couple of days.

00:01:30.319 --> 00:01:30.640
No.

00:01:31.319 --> 00:01:32.640
I have to talk to him right now.

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:33.719
I can't wait another second.

00:01:33.719 --> 00:01:34.560
Look what time it is.

00:01:34.719 --> 00:01:35.920
Where are you going to find him?

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.439
Then tomorrow.

00:01:38.719 --> 00:01:40.000
Help me get him to come out tomorrow.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:40.920
I need to have a serious talk with him.

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:42.000
Wait, don't you have his number?

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:43.120
I don't want to speak to him.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.959
What exactly is going on between you two?

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:50.079
Chen Fan

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:51.840
I know you broke up.

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:52.719
You're feeling upset.

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:53.920
But you called me over here,

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:55.560
just to watch you act out your heartbreak?

00:01:55.879 --> 00:01:56.519
Broke up?

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:57.359
Who's heartbroken?

00:01:57.359 --> 00:01:58.359
Didn't you and Ruochu already...

00:01:58.359 --> 00:01:59.599
You have the nerve to mention Ruochu?

00:01:59.879 --> 00:02:02.000
Then let me settle this with you, Zhou Honghai.

00:02:02.319 --> 00:02:03.480
I call you "Brother,"

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:04.599
treat you politely every day,

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:05.319
and this is how you treat me?

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:06.920
How did I treat you?

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:08.919
Sending her back so late last night.

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:09.919
What were you two doing?

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:11.280
I just had a meal with her,

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:12.599
and then took her home. So what?

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.000
Even if there really was something between us,

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.039
it's not up to you, the dumped ex-boyfriend,

00:02:16.039 --> 00:02:16.960
to be pointing fingers here, right?

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:18.560
I didn't agree, so we didn't break up.

00:02:19.159 --> 00:02:20.680
You have the nerve to have something with her?

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:23.120
Stealing your brother's girl, aren't you ashamed?

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:23.960
Chen Fan, calm down.

00:02:24.439 --> 00:02:25.879
Brother Honghai isn't the type to take advantage of people.

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:27.520
No, how did I take advantage?

00:02:27.639 --> 00:02:28.879
And how did I steal your girl?

00:02:29.199 --> 00:02:31.479
It was him not cherishing that girl,

00:02:31.479 --> 00:02:32.240
breaking her heart.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.120
Now you're blaming me?

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:35.080
So you rushed in to cherish her?

00:02:35.319 --> 00:02:36.400
We haven't even cleared things up yet,

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:37.080
and you're throwing yourself at her.

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.759
You call that not taking advantage?

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:41.719
I saw through you a long time ago.

00:02:41.719 --> 00:02:43.400
You have hundreds of schemes spinning in your head daily.

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:45.319
I bet Ruochu has already seen clearly

00:02:45.319 --> 00:02:46.000
what kind of person you are.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:46.840
Alright.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.159
If this goes on,

00:02:48.159 --> 00:02:49.360
we really can't be brothers anymore.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:51.319
Aren't we here to pick a game today?

00:02:52.919 --> 00:02:53.759
The two proposals for this game,

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:54.840
we've studied them both.

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.400
This one is mine.

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:57.719
This one is Brother Honghai's.

00:02:58.879 --> 00:02:59.280
Choose yours.

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:00.159
Why?

00:03:00.159 --> 00:03:01.400
Making private server plugins is illegal.

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:03.080
Fine.

00:03:03.759 --> 00:03:05.479
Then let's make translation patches for overseas games.

00:03:05.479 --> 00:03:06.639
And add a paid unlock for the story.

00:03:06.639 --> 00:03:07.120
Is that okay?

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:07.439
That's not okay either.

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.719
The cyber police are cracking down hard lately.

00:03:09.719 --> 00:03:10.919
You want to walk right into the line of fire?

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:12.680
I prefer Brother Liang's proposal.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.960
We have to start with a low-cost shooting mini-game.

00:03:16.439 --> 00:03:17.960
The cyber police can't check everything.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:19.319
As long as our tech is solid

00:03:19.479 --> 00:03:19.960
and we hide deep enough,

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:20.680
who can catch us?

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:23.120
Solid tech must be used on the right path.

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:24.560
That's why I said,

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:26.360
people like you with minds full of crooked thoughts...

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:27.400
You towards Ruochu, you just...

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:28.560
Chen Fan, talk about the game.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:32.479
Have you seen his proposal?

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:33.960
Simple plot,

00:03:33.960 --> 00:03:34.439
rough characters.

00:03:34.439 --> 00:03:35.199
Who would play it?

00:03:35.319 --> 00:03:36.360
Simple games can also go viral.

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:37.919
You forgot there was a shooting game before

00:03:37.919 --> 00:03:39.840
even simpler than this that went viral.

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.280
Millions of downloads in just a few days.

00:03:41.639 --> 00:03:42.159
What was it?

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:46.840
My point is, simple games can also be hits

00:03:47.159 --> 00:03:47.520
No

00:03:48.199 --> 00:03:49.360
Why would people ignore Legend

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:50.280
And not play World of Magical Beasts

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.280
To waste time here

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:54.000
Brother Honghai, although my game is simple

00:03:54.240 --> 00:03:55.280
Its advantage is its small size

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:57.120
Even low-spec computers can run it smoothly

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.120
And the production cycle is short

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:00.479
Chen Fan

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:02.840
Brother Honghai just wants to make a profit quickly

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:05.120
Shouldn't we think of a compromise

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:05.639
Can't do it

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:07.120
Understood

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:09.840
So I spent all this effort making a plan

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.520
Just to hear you two singing the same tune here, right

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:12.120
No, no

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:12.879
Chen Fan

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.599
I know because of Ruochu

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:15.360
You have a problem with me

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:16.639
You're just contradicting me, right

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:19.240
I am a professional

00:04:19.439 --> 00:04:21.040
I've made more games than you've eaten

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:25.639
Anyway, I can't explain it clearly to someone

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:27.680
With a mind full of crooked thoughts like you

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:28.839
Do you understand

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:32.680
Fine

00:04:34.319 --> 00:04:36.360
In the whole world, you, Chen Fan, are the most professional

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:37.439
You are the most high-minded

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.160
When this lousy game of yours fails

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:40.680
I'll see how you keep acting high and mighty

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:41.839
Brother Honghai

00:04:41.839 --> 00:04:42.399
Let him go

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.040
Feifan Tech won't stop turning without him

00:04:50.079 --> 00:04:50.360
Hello

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.680
Zhou Honghai, right

00:04:51.879 --> 00:04:53.959
We met last night at Long's Group office

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:54.720
Hello, hello

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:55.519
Hello, President Liu

00:04:58.439 --> 00:04:59.639
Yes, understood, okay

00:05:00.199 --> 00:05:00.600
Good

00:05:06.759 --> 00:05:07.519
Chen Fan

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:10.600
Since you don't know what's good for you, don't blame me

00:05:19.639 --> 00:05:19.959
Wait

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.279
Where did you go yesterday, kid

00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:22.199
Why weren't you with us

00:05:22.319 --> 00:05:22.720
Yeah

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.199
I called you so many times and no one answered

00:05:24.279 --> 00:05:26.959
Don't ask, I was watching the venue at the club yesterday

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:29.040
And my phone got water damaged

00:05:29.519 --> 00:05:31.279
Then I went straight to the internet cafe to check the accounts

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:33.279
I was so sleepy

00:05:33.279 --> 00:05:34.839
I just fell asleep on that sofa

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:36.160
It's just a phone

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:36.920
I'll buy you another one

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:38.439
You can pick whatever you want, no matter how expensive

00:05:38.439 --> 00:05:38.800
Really

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:39.959
Pick one

00:05:39.959 --> 00:05:40.839
Hey, then I'm really going to pick one

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.639
My code is at a critical point

00:05:43.639 --> 00:05:44.720
Don't cause trouble

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.199
Liang, what are you working on now

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:47.879
Is it that antivirus software from before

00:05:47.879 --> 00:05:49.879
No, that software is pretty mature now

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:52.160
I'm making a game to test the waters

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.160
Challenging a new field

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:54.439
You know how to do this too

00:05:54.439 --> 00:05:56.519
Yeah, the gaming market is hot right now

00:05:56.759 --> 00:05:57.879
We have to strike while the iron is hot

00:05:58.279 --> 00:05:59.560
But this game I'm making

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:01.439
Is just the most ordinary shooting game

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:03.439
Simple is good

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.519
I suggest the game memory usage must be small

00:06:05.879 --> 00:06:07.560
Even in the trashiest illegal internet cafes

00:06:07.560 --> 00:06:08.360
It should run easily

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:09.319
So I changed this part

00:06:09.519 --> 00:06:10.160
Do you see

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:11.680
Look here

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:13.680
If you change this part like this

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:15.720
Once you two start talking tech

00:06:16.079 --> 00:06:17.480
I can't get a word in

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:19.680
Then you go to sleep

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:20.759
You're so sleepy anyway

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:21.480
Go to sleep quickly

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:22.480
Okay, okay, okay

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:23.319
Then I'm going to sleep

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:24.079
Goodnight

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:25.160
Sleeping

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.240
Right, right, right

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.439
This... this can also be done like this

00:06:27.439 --> 00:06:28.040
This works, this works

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:31.519
Su Ruochu

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:34.680
Enter all these files before you get off work

00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:37.199
New company rule: the building gets locked after seven

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:37.959
No one can stay

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:44.160
This way, there's no chance to look for clues

00:06:44.439 --> 00:06:46.480
Looks like I need to find another way

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:05.519
In my past life

00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:07.600
I was threatened right here in this law firm

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.560
And hit by a car on this very road

00:07:14.399 --> 00:07:16.360
It's okay. It's still early

00:07:16.759 --> 00:07:18.759
Since those documents were handed to me at the firm

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:20.279
There must be a copy archived here

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:22.399
I have to find a way to get it

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.319
Sorry about that

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:28.519
Sorry, are you okay?

00:07:29.959 --> 00:07:32.399
You're that girl from Luocheng Computer Academy

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:36.959
I did have someone install some things last week

00:07:37.639 --> 00:07:39.160
He said some settings needed changing

00:07:41.319 --> 00:07:43.879
You're the girl who came to fix the computer

00:07:44.199 --> 00:07:44.920
How come you're here?

00:07:45.160 --> 00:07:46.720
I'm interning here

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:47.959
In charge of organizing case files

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:50.279
Then where are you going in such a rush?

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:53.319
Don't ask. I was wrongly accused

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:54.800
They said I lost important data inside this

00:07:55.279 --> 00:07:56.360
And that I broke the machine

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.879
Now the machine won't turn on

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:59.360
I have no way to prove myself

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:00.600
I just thought I'd hurry out

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.680
And find someone to fix it for me

00:08:02.439 --> 00:08:02.959
By the way

00:08:03.399 --> 00:08:04.480
Last time in Luocheng

00:08:04.959 --> 00:08:06.519
That guy who fixed my computer

00:08:06.519 --> 00:08:07.680
Can you help me contact him?

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:12.800
We haven't seen each other in a long time

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:15.680
Please think of a way to contact him for me

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:17.079
Fate brought us together

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:19.959
You wouldn't want to see me wrongly accused, right?

00:08:22.439 --> 00:08:23.279
Alright

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:30.319
I can't believe you guys are also from Yunhai University

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:32.320
Little brother, thanks for last time

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:33.840
I'm Xu Qiuci

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:35.120
Senior, I'm Chen Fan

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:36.720
What's going on with this?

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:38.000
Ruochu, you tell him

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:40.000
I get so angry just mentioning it

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:43.799
It's like this

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:45.519
Senior Xu

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:47.039
Is interning at a law firm

00:08:47.039 --> 00:08:49.960
A Lawyer Sun at the firm asked her to organize files

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:50.840
Which included

00:08:50.840 --> 00:08:52.159
The videos inside this DV camera

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:53.679
But when she returned it

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:56.639
That Lawyer Sun insisted she made a mistake

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:58.519
And deleted that key video

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.360
Now this DV camera is broken too

00:09:00.639 --> 00:09:02.799
So Senior Xu can't prove her innocence

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.000
The content of this video

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:07.039
Do you remember what it was?

00:09:07.320 --> 00:09:08.080
I don't remember

00:09:08.559 --> 00:09:09.679
That bastard...

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.399
That Lawyer Sun

00:09:12.879 --> 00:09:13.799
He didn't say

00:09:13.799 --> 00:09:15.279
But I heard from other colleagues

00:09:15.519 --> 00:09:18.519
It seems related to the land acquisition in the old district

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:20.360
The old district

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:24.000
Longshi Real Estate was suspected of violent acquisition

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:25.200
Finally, due to insufficient evidence

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:26.360
It was a case where they avoided prosecution

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:28.200
Yes, you know that case

00:09:28.679 --> 00:09:30.639
That case caused quite a stir back then

00:09:30.879 --> 00:09:32.320
It seems our firm handled it

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.480
When our seniors went to investigate

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.600
They took this very DV camera

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.279
These people from Longshi

00:09:38.559 --> 00:09:39.759
When I went to see Old Master Tang before

00:09:39.759 --> 00:09:41.080
To buy Yunmeng Paradise

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:43.159
I saw their people strong-arming a sale there too

00:09:43.639 --> 00:09:45.519
Senior, think carefully

00:09:45.679 --> 00:09:46.679
Besides this matter

00:09:46.879 --> 00:09:48.200
Are there any other suspicious points?

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:52.159
Also, that Lawyer Sun

00:09:52.320 --> 00:09:53.519
He suddenly acted out of character

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:54.639
He became very fierce

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:57.240
He threatened that if I didn't admit my mistake

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.240
He would tell the school

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:00.679
That I caused a huge loss to the firm

00:10:00.679 --> 00:10:02.159
Say I committed a major work error

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:04.200
And make the school give me a serious demerit

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:06.840
This guy

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:09.039
Why do I feel like he's forcing you

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.360
To take the blame for this?

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:14.440
I'm just guessing

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:17.480
Senior

00:10:17.919 --> 00:10:19.919
I'll fix this machine for you within three days

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:20.960
But I have a condition

00:10:21.159 --> 00:10:22.240
Any condition is fine

00:10:23.919 --> 00:10:25.759
I want you to sit down and have a good talk with me

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:27.759
Just once

00:10:28.679 --> 00:10:29.159
Is that okay?

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.120
Just that? What kind of condition is that?

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:36.399
Ruochu, agree to it

00:10:42.919 --> 00:10:44.519
Actually, I've wanted to talk to you for a long time.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:45.919
But I was afraid I...

00:10:46.159 --> 00:10:47.919
I... I couldn't control my emotions...

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:49.559
And would put pressure on you.

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:51.159
I'm sorry, Chen Fan.

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:52.440
You don't need to apologize to me.

00:10:53.519 --> 00:10:54.639
I just want to know why.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:58.679
Is it because of Zhou Honghai?

00:10:58.879 --> 00:11:00.120
This was my own decision.

00:11:00.840 --> 00:11:02.120
It has nothing to do with him.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:05.120
So, why exactly is it?